{#-
  Switch — native <input type="checkbox" role="switch"> with a thumb-on-rails
  visual envelope. Animated thumb slide + bg color (180 ms base / standard
  easing per 14-motion-baseline.md §Switch).

  Doctrine (OQ-8): native checkbox with `role="switch"` rather than the
  button-pattern `<button role=switch aria-pressed>`. Reasons:
    - 100 % keyboard-complete (Space toggles natively)
    - autofill works
    - form-data inclusion in POST is automatic
    - aria-checked is browser-managed (no manual stamping)
  See STATE.md S1.3 §"Resolved at session opening" / OQ-8 for the full record.

  Two rendering modes (mirrors Checkbox):
    1. `label` set        → <label class="cremona-switch-row"> wraps input + track
                            + thumb + label text (standalone usage).
    2. `label` not set    → <span class="cremona-switch-wrap"> bare layout
                            (Field / DataTable composition).

  Parameters (enumerated):
    name             (string, optional)  — form field name
    htmlId           (string, optional)  — id; required when paired with external Label.for
    value            (string, optional)  — value when checked (defaults to "on")
    checked          (bool,   optional)
    label            (string, optional)  — inline label text; if set → row mode
    description      (string, optional)  — short caption below the label (row mode only)
    size             (string, optional)  — sm (default — 32×18 track) | md (44×24 track)
    required         (bool,   optional)  — sets HTML `required` + aria-required="true"
    disabled         (bool,   optional)
    invalid          (bool,   optional)  — aria-invalid="true" + danger border
    describedBy      (string, optional)  — space-separated ids for aria-describedby
    ariaLabel        (string, optional)  — accessible name when bare mode + no external label
    className        (string, optional)
-#}

{%- set name          = name          | default(null) -%}
{%- set htmlId        = htmlId        | default(null) -%}
{%- set value         = value         | default(null) -%}
{%- set checked       = checked       | default(false) -%}
{%- set label         = label         | default(null) -%}
{%- set description   = description   | default(null) -%}
{%- set size          = size          | default('sm') -%}
{%- set required      = required      | default(false) -%}
{%- set disabled      = disabled      | default(false) -%}
{%- set invalid       = invalid       | default(false) -%}
{%- set describedBy   = describedBy   | default(null) -%}
{%- set ariaLabel     = ariaLabel     | default(null) -%}
{%- set className     = className     | default('') -%}

{%- set _rootClasses = [label ? 'cremona-switch-row' : 'cremona-switch-wrap'] -%}
{%- if disabled -%}{%- set _rootClasses = _rootClasses | merge(['cremona-switch-row--disabled']) -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if invalid  -%}{%- set _rootClasses = _rootClasses | merge(['cremona-switch-row--invalid']) -%}{%- endif -%}
{%- if className -%}{%- set _rootClasses = _rootClasses | merge([className]) -%}{%- endif -%}

{%- set _tag = label ? 'label' : 'span' -%}

<{{ _tag }}
  class="{{ _rootClasses | join(' ') }}"
  data-size="{{ size }}"
  {%- if disabled %} data-state="disabled"{% endif -%}
>
  <span class="cremona-switch" data-size="{{ size }}">
    <input
      type="checkbox"
      role="switch"
      class="cremona-switch__input"
      {%- if htmlId %} id="{{ htmlId }}"{% endif -%}
      {%- if name %} name="{{ name }}"{% endif -%}
      {%- if value is not null %} value="{{ value }}"{% endif -%}
      {%- if checked %} checked{% endif -%}
      {%- if required %} required aria-required="true"{% endif -%}
      {%- if disabled %} disabled{% endif -%}
      {%- if invalid %} aria-invalid="true"{% endif -%}
      {%- if describedBy %} aria-describedby="{{ describedBy }}"{% endif -%}
      {%- if ariaLabel %} aria-label="{{ ariaLabel }}"{% endif -%}
    >
    <span class="cremona-switch__track" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="cremona-switch__thumb"></span>
    </span>
  </span>
  {%- if label -%}
    <span class="cremona-switch-row__text">
      <span class="cremona-switch-row__label">{{ label }}</span>
      {%- if required -%}
        <span class="cremona-switch-row__required" aria-hidden="true">*</span>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if description -%}
        <span class="cremona-switch-row__description">{{ description }}</span>
      {%- endif -%}
    </span>
  {%- endif -%}
</{{ _tag }}>
